Package: blocklength
Type: Package
Title: Select Optimal Block-Length to Bootstrap Dependent Data (Block Bootstrap)
Version: 0.0.0.9005
Authors@R: c(
             person("Alec", "Stashevsky",
                    email = "alec@alecstashevsky.com",
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Sergio", "Armella",
                    role = "ctb")
            )
Maintainer: Alec Stashevsky <alec@alecstashevsky.com>
Description: A set of functions to select the optimal block-length for a 
    dependent bootstrap (block-bootstrap). Includes the Hall, Horowitz, and Jing
    (1995) cross-validation method and the Politis and White (2004) Spectral 
    Density Plug-in method with a corresponding set of S3 plot methods.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
